headline: Tyson Foods AGM: Shareholders Elect Directors, Approve Pay Plan, Reject Waste Lagoon Proposal
summary: Tyson Foods (NYSE:TSN) shareholders voted to elect directors, ratify the company’s auditor, approve updates to an equity incentive plan, and endorse executive compensation at the company’s 63rd annual meeting on Feb. 5 in Springdale, Arkansas. Shareholders also voted down three shareholder proposals
